   The accounts of widespread Iranian resistance stood in sharp
contrast to last fall's similar attack on Iranian offshore
platforms. During that operation, Iranians heeded warnings to
abandon the platforms and did not confront U.S. warships directly.
   Carlucci, while stressing he had few details, acknowledged this
