<HEAD>AT&T Chairman Dead</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Leads with 13 grafs to recast lede, add analyst's comments,
background; picks up 8th graf, Olson, a native xxx; SUBS last graf
to add detail on survivors; adds byline; Version moved on business
