<TEXT>
   A trade association, U.S. Wheat Associates
Inc., has helped launch an olympian effort in South Korea to
promote high-quality bread and other bakery products.
   The beginning of the yearlong promotion will coincide with the
1988 summer Olympic Games in Seoul and will have ``International
