belief that cooperative ventures in foreign countries can expand
markets in the face of stiff competition from other exporting
nations.''
   Ten major South Korean cities were selected as sites for bakery
fairs to display products for consumers and the news media.
   Also, in-store bakery promotions through the 1,000 selected
bakeries will aim at a sales target of $30 million to $50 million
over the yearlong campaign, the association said.
